Analyze the following PlantUML use case model and detect if it contains any antipatterns.
Base your analysis solely on the model provided. Do not use any outside knowledge.


PlantUML Model:
@startuml
' Version 1 – contains Functional Decomposition: Using the include relationship

actor Customer
actor "Event Organizer" as Organizer

rectangle "Event Ticketing System" {
  usecase "Browse Events" as UC1
  usecase "Purchase Ticket" as UC2
  usecase "Validate Payment Details" as UC3
  usecase "Cancel Ticket" as UC4
  usecase "Create Event" as UC5
  usecase "View Sales Report" as UC6
